headline: QUALCOMM (NasdaqGS:QCOM) Extends Alphawave Acquisition Discussions Deadline
summary: QUALCOMM (NasdaqGS:QCOM) has been in discussions regarding a potential acquisition of Alphawave IP Group, with extended deadlines highlighting the ongoing interest. This news emerged amidst broader market growth of 2% over the past week and a 12% increase over the last year. Concurrently, QUALCOMM's share price rose 5% over the past month.
